{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "empback-api-collection",
		"name": "EmpBack API Ecosystem",
		"description": "Comprehensive API collection for the EmpBack Learning & Career Platform.\n\n## Features Covered\n- **Authentication**: Users (Students, Job Seekers, Professionals) & Admins\n- **Core Entities**: Courses, Jobs, Internships, Mentors, Companies\n- **Business Logic**: \n    - Job Applications (ATS)\n    - Mentorship Booking & Slot Management\n    - Course Enrollment\n    - Admin Moderation (Approve/Reject)\n\n## Pre-configured Environments\nThis collection uses a global variable `baseUrl`. \n- Default: `http://localhost:3000/api`\n\n## Automated Token Management\nLogin requests contain **Tests** scripts that automatically save the `token` to your environment variable. You don't need to copy-paste tokens manually!",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "1. Authentication (Start Here)",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login - Student (John)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"pm.environment.set(\"token\", jsonData.token);",
									"console.log(\"Token updated for Student\");"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"student@test.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/login",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"users",
								"login"
							]
						},
						"description": "Login as a Student user. \n**Credentials**: student@test.com / password123\n**Effect**: Automatically sets the `token` variable."
					},
					"response": []
				},
